{"tid":372781,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"咩叫「如入鮑魚之肆，久而不聞其臭」","createTime":"2017-08-24T14:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T14:29:14.000Z","uid":119834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b691cee6f5d8795c95e2de09f41d3162fa79e27","tid":372781,"uid":119834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"孔子曰：「與善人居，如入芝蘭之室，久而不聞其香，即與之化矣；與不善人居，<span style=\"color: red;\">如入鮑魚之肆，久而不聞其臭</span>，亦與之化矣。」<br />\n<br />\n原來孔子二千幾年前食臭鮑已經咁有經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531881d0fdc11184a53ba4401be715ed11de2434","tid":372781,"uid":53164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:25:23.000Z","msg":"古代嘅鮑魚=咸魚"},{"pid":"ccd151935ecee41ecf5f4fcba7d932fc9fc4f96d","tid":372781,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea31e12e09a5952389a74a3ae9ac61179ab8e8c5","tid":372781,"uid":119834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:29:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古代嘅鮑魚=咸魚</blockquote><br />\n條女又臭鮑又成條咸魚咁 咁都幾難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}